projects.name: Student Job Portal
projects.description: Designed and developed a robust student job portal using Java technologies, facilitating seamless job search and recruitment processes for students and employers. Integrated advanced search and filtering functionalities to match students with relevant job opportunities based on their skills and preferences. Utilized object-oriented programming principles to build a scalable and maintainable codebase, enabling easy adaptation to evolving requirements.
